  { q: 'Are you really available 24/7 for emergency AC repair?', a: 'Yes — we run a true after-hours dispatch line. Call (813) 395-2324 any time day or night. During heat waves our technicians often work past midnight to clear the queue.' },
  { q: 'How fast can you get to my house?', a: 'From Wesley Chapel we can typically reach anywhere in Pasco, Hillsborough and Polk counties within 60–90 minutes of the call. Central Tampa, New Tampa and Land O\' Lakes are often faster.' },
  { q: 'What counts as an AC emergency?', a: 'No cooling during summer heat (especially with infants, elderly residents, or pets), water leaks actively damaging flooring or drywall, electrical smells or smoke from the air handler, or a completely dead system in a storm-damaged home.' },
  { q: 'How much does emergency AC repair cost after hours?', a: 'Emergency service carries a modest after-hours dispatch fee on top of the flat-rate repair price. We quote the full number before any work — no meter-running hourly billing.' },
